    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Find the truth. Lose yourself.</i></h2>Your little brother disappears. In his room, you find his odd drawings of the abandoned castle at the edge of your town. When you flip one of the drawings, you read: &quot;The castle won't let me leave. Please, brother, help me.&quot;<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395520/extras/a914e2800e6131580b022c93aed92905.poster.avif?t=1724350640\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395520/extras/a914e2800e6131580b022c93aed92905.webm?t=1724350640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395520/extras/a914e2800e6131580b022c93aed92905.mp4?t=1724350640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bring pictures to life</h2>Solve beatiful and meditative puzzles by matching pictures with the world. Please your inner explorer and enjoy stunning hand-crafted castle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395520/extras/62d8d89cf6ab5e8a51af89a2362eb0ab.poster.avif?t=1724350640\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395520/extras/62d8d89cf6ab5e8a51af89a2362eb0ab.webm?t=1724350640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395520/extras/62d8d89cf6ab5e8a51af89a2362eb0ab.mp4?t=1724350640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Eerie yet home-like atmosphere</h2>Whimsical as childhood and uncanny as shadows under the bed. The castle doesn't scary you — it lures you in and want you to stay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395520/extras/54ccaf811553b090176ad2ac867bd399.poster.avif?t=1724350640\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395520/extras/54ccaf811553b090176ad2ac867bd399.webm?t=1724350640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395520/extras/54ccaf811553b090176ad2ac867bd399.mp4?t=1724350640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
